name: Cone + Pyramid ##1
description:
The basic principle of visualization of objects is a recreate usual 3D objects such as a ball, cube, cone, cylinder, pyramid... in a new visual language form with lines.

The basic concept is to recreate a 3D object from all sides. We cannot see the object completely in space, there will always be a part that we cannot see. This is a visual model of how an object looks from all sides in space through lines.
